         <abstract id="aspace_42605b870c8be59c34b31eb0feade9ea">The papers consist of correspondence, writings, printed material, newspaper clippings, and photographs documenting the life and career of Samuel F. Pryor and his friendship with Charles and Anne Morrow Lindbergh.</abstract>
